    dc:creator "Hazzi, Nicolás A.; Valderrama-Ardila, Carlos; Brescovit Daniele Polotow, Antonio D.; Simó, Miguel" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "New records and geographical distribution of ctenid spiders (Araneae: Ctenidae) in Colombia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222227> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222227>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 5. Distribution of ctenids in Colombia. 2, Ancylometes bogotensis (circles) and A. rufus (triangles); 3, Caloctenus aculeatus; 4, distribution of Centroctenus occeliventer; 5, Ctenus amphora (circles), Ctenus inaja (squares) and Ctenus villasboasi (triangle). Gray circles: previous records. Black circles: new records" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222227/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

